{"tid":2273332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"宣布暫停4國公民入境 習近平罕見撤換12名駐外大使","createTime":"2020-11-05T15:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T00:57:27.000Z","uid":7736,"like":120,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"3e90d56d435f069d6984888653bc09696aa4a14c","tid":2273332,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"中共突宣布 暫停英印孟菲4國公民入境<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中共第十九屆五中全會剛落幕就傳出多起權鬥訊息，中共總書記習近平今天罕見將12名駐外大使免職，官方並宣布暫停英國、菲律賓、孟加拉、印度等國民眾入境中國，引發外界聯想。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《環球時報》報導，中國領導人習近平今天根據中國人民代表大會常務委員會的決定，撤換中國12名駐外大使，並改派他人履新，包括巴基斯坦、斯里蘭卡、土耳其、衣索比亞、馬達加斯加、聖多美普林西比、幾內亞比索、白羅斯、亞美尼亞、匈牙利、賽普勒斯、千里達及托巴哥。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中國駐英國、菲律賓、孟加拉、印度大使館已陸續公告「暫停使用部分有效中國簽證通知」，上述4國持有效中國簽證、居留許可的公民暫停入境中國，持有外交、公務、禮遇等簽證人員不受禁令影響，中方指出，外國人如有緊急或特殊原因需要趕赴中國，可向駐館申請簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3343277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3343277&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8h5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=aebe1d12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3343277&h=074f33b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3343277</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.us.sina.com/gb/international/phoenixtv/2020-11-05/detail-ihacruyi7379194.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.us.sina.com%2Fgb%2Finternational%2Fphoenixtv%2F2020-11-05%2Fdetail-ihacruyi7379194.shtml&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8h5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=7946db56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.us.sina.com/gb/international/phoenixtv/2020-11-05/detail-ihacruyi7379194.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"b422efd78d8fc42dc8c9d7a9b49f6797ece8800d","tid":2273332,"uid":173207,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"3e90d56d435f069d6984888653bc09696aa4a14c","tid":2273332,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:55:08.000Z